gdlex-ocr (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add File > Exit with Ctrl+Q and improve Linux desktop integration.
  * Open generated outputs through Qt desktop services.
  * Add application identity, splash, tray icon, and Debian payload tests.
  * Allow disabling the splash screen with GDLEX_OCR_DISABLE_SPLASH.
  * Use raster icons for the splash screen and system tray.

